    "However, pretraining a DRL agent using a model contradicts the advantages of DRL being \"model-free\" because BPS models can be time-consuming to develop.",
    "Therefore, further research could usefully explore the use of simpler and a lower level of detail models for the offline training of DRL agents for building controls.",
